<Defs>
  <ThingDef ParentName="PhotonozoaThingBase">
    <defName>Harpactotyrannus</defName>
    <label>harpactotyrannus</label>
    <description>Born in the forge of an ancient machine-god, Harpactotyrannus is not a creature of nature, but of design — the living code of the Eternal Hunt. It moves with mechanical precision and strikes with divine fury, a perfect engine of motion and mastery. Where it walks, armies fall and predators remember fear.
	
	To watch it hunt is to see entropy undone — a flawless equilibrium of speed and violence, forever optimized for the kill. It is the Beast of the Eternal Hunt, knowing neither mercy nor purpose… only the pursuit that never ends.</description>
